1. Describe application state as plain objects and arrays.
2. Describe changes in the system as plain objects.
3. Describe the logic for handling changes as pure functions.

1. 用普通对象描述应用状态
2. 用普通对象描述系统内的改变
3. 用纯函数描述处理改变的逻辑

The tradeoff that Redux offers is to add indirection to decouple “what happened” from “how things change”.

Redux将“发生的事情”与“事情如何改变”脱钩